    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，加拿大，墨西哥的关税随着时间的流逝而“可能会增加”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-says-canada-mexico-tariffs-could-go-up-over-time</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，对墨西哥和加拿大的关税可能高于本周早些时候征收的25％的税率，这将进一步的不确定性注入了贸易政策，这些政策使市场震撼，并使企业处于边缘状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-says-canada-mexico-tariffs-could-go-up-over-time</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 11:50:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的偶然，不合时宜的关税策略播下了混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-s-on-again-off-again-tariff-strategy-sows-confusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统疯狂的关税弹幕的逆转和错误的推出，使我们的贸易伙伴和企业感到困惑，同时提出了有关其签名政策目标的疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/trump-s-on-again-off-again-tariff-strategy-sows-confusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
